## Management Areas

### Social Management
- **Communities**: Create and manage community spaces
- **Posts & Comments**: Moderate user-generated content
- **User Analytics**: Track engagement and community health

### Chat Management  
- **Channels**: Moderate chat channels and conversations
- **Messages**: Review and manage chat content
- **Member Management**: Control channel membership and permissions

### System Administration
- **Security Settings**: API keys, authentication, and access control
- **Push Notifications**: Certificate management and testing
- **Webhooks**: Real-time event configuration

