## Moderation via API

Many of the moderation functions supported in SP Console's UI interface are exposed as APIs accessible with an Admin Access Token. If you would like to moderate some features this way instead of using the console, please refer to the[ **Social Plus API documentation**](../social+-apis-and-services/).
